cat /etc/hosts

cacheType=''

timeout(){
        waitfor=600
        command=$*
        sleeppid=$PPID
        ($command) &
        commandpid=$!
        ( sleep $waitfor ; kill -9 $commandpid) &
        watchdog=$!
        wait $commandpid > /dev/null 2>&1
        commandcode=$?
        echo "依赖安装执行状态码上报：$commandcode"
        if [ $commandcode -eq 1 ] || [ $commandcode -eq 137 ]
        then
             echo '安装依赖发生错误'
             kill  -9 $watchdog > /dev/null 2>&1
	         exit 1
        fi
        kill  -9 $watchdog > /dev/null 2>&1
}

install(){
    if [ $cacheType = 'yarn-cache' ]
    then
        yarn install --production=false 
    else
        mnpm install --production=false
    fi
    
}

makeCacheType(){
    if [ -e 'yarn.lock' ];
	then
		cacheType='yarn-cache'
	elif [ -e 'package-lock.json' -o -e 'npm-shrinkwrap.json' ];
	then
		cacheType='npm-cache'
	else
		cacheType='yarn-cache'
	fi
}

cacheClean() {
    echo "尝试清理依赖缓存"
    # 后台执行清理项目依赖
    ( rm -rf node_modules ) &
    # 后台执行清理 yarn or mnpm 全局缓存
    if [ $cacheType = 'yarn-cache' ]
    then
        ( yarn cache clean ) &
    else
        ( mnpm cache clean --force ) &
    fi
    wait
    echo "缓存清理完成"
}

cd ${projectRoot:-.}

makeCacheType

if [ -e node_modules ];
then
    echo "node_modules exist will not get cache"
else
    if [ -e /bin/get-cache ];
    then
        get-cache $cacheType
    fi
fi

( 
  timeout install
) || (
  echo 'Yarn RUN Something Error, Try Again'
  cacheClean
  timeout install
) || (
  echo 'Yarn RUN Something Error, Try Third'
  cacheClean
  timeout install
)

'''
